  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study aims to confirm that a reduced dosage of GCSF is effective in preventing febrile
      neutropenia among patients with breast cancer, treated with chemotherapy and presenting with
      a low to moderate risk of developing febrile neutropenia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
